Core issue: better-sqlite3 native addon is x86_64, Mac is arm64e.
Every new Database() call crashes on Apple Silicon.

Fixes:
- loadSessionsFromDb: secondary sqlite3 CLI path for message counts + source
- /api/sessions/:id/messages: export CLI fallback (60s timeout)
- /api/usage/:days: delegate to hermes insights CLI
- /api/usage/daily/:days: sqlite3 CLI query for daily aggregates
- loadSessionsFromDbCli: exclude cron sessions, add source field
- sendViaWebSocket: 15s timeout so CLI fallback runs on WS failure
- normalizeSource: null source → 'cli' instead of 'other'
